org.gephi.graph.api.types

Interface TimeSet<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - key type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntervalSet, TimestampSet

    public interface TimeSet<K>
    Interface that defines the functionalities both timestamp and interval set have.
